al</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Chesnal Dey Arepalli</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Waqas Shuaib</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Anuj Tewari</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Faisal Khosa</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">2014Dec1 | American Journal of Roentgenology, Vol. 203, No. 6</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.2214/AJR.13.12323">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.1007/978-3-642-37393-0_239-1"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.1007/978-3-642-37393-0_239-1">Evaluation and Treatment of Gastrointestinal Angiodysplasia</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">T. Gregory Walker</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Keith Quencer</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">14 July 2014</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/978-3-642-37393-0_239-1">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.4329/wjr.v6.i4.82"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.4329/wjr.v6.i4.82">Role of interventional radiology in the management of acute gastrointestinal bleeding</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Raja S Ramaswamy</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">2014Jan1 | World Journal of Radiology, Vol. 6, No. 4</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.4329/wjr.v6.i4.82">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.1148/rg.335135019"><div class="rela